# Prompt templates
NEWS_ENHANCEMENT_PROMPT=Write a brief, factual news summary (200-300 characters) based on this headline: '{headline}' and these details: '{summary}'

Your summary must:
1. Be concise but informative (200-300 characters)
2. Focus only on the key facts
3. Use journalistic language
4. Avoid speculation or opinions
5. Start immediately with content without any meta-text

DO NOT use phrases like "In this summary" or "I will provide" - just write the summary directly.

